description:
We decided to sneak in a 4v4 rematch with the same Teams while we wait for the Season 5 FFA to happen. The goal is to kill or outlive the other team.

This game we used a freshly generated, random map to prevent the problems mcedit caused us last time. Basically we all started at spawn and walked 2 opposite directions to make a little bit of distance between us. We agreed to stay within -1000 to 1000 for the X and Z coordinated and not to attack each other during the first day.

The only way to recover health in this is with golden apples or instant health potions. Golden apples require a 8 gold ingots (instead of nuggets) and an apple to craft. Glistering Melons require 1 gold block (instead of 1 nugget) and a melon. Health does not recover from keeping your hunger bar full.

(Team: DOOKE)
